data.description: This beautifully designed 2 bedroom, 2 bath ranch-style home offers spectacular panoramic mountain views, abundant natural lighting, and a gorgeous, grassy backyard with custom pathway and expanded patio. The open concept living boasts a large glass slider, modern LVP flooring, a charming wood burning stove, and a gourmet kitchen with a pantry, upgraded appliances, immaculate counters and perfectly matched finishes! Take in the mountain views from your large windows in the primary bedroom suite with a spa-like bathroom and plenty of closet space. This home has all the upgrades you desire and more! 2 car garage on a large lot with an oversized shed in the backyard can hold projects, tools, and gardening equipment. Close to dining, hiking, biking, & golf.
